=== Verb ===
[[Category:Spanish verbs]]

==== Transitive ====
'''sacar'''
# to [[remove]]
# to [[obtain]]
# to stick out
# to [[take]] (as in a [[photograph]])
# to [[make]] (as in a [[copy]])

==== Intransitive ====
'''sacar'''
# (''sports'') to [[serve]]
# (''[[soccer]], [[football]]'') to [[kick off]]

